<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[Shell the peas, keeping a handful of pods.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Boil the shells in salted water for 30-45 mins]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Sauté the onion and pancetta (if using), until golden, 5 mins.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Add the peas the first lot of parsley, and a ladleful of hot broth. Cook 10 mins.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Meanwhile whiz the pods and their water, then mix well with the stock and add to peas.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Add the rice, and cook until done mixing every so often.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[When cooked add in a ladleful of broth, the butter, the second lot of parsley, and the cheese]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
